<header class="site-header h-card">
	<div class="avatar">
		<img src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, Tomie.Users.User.avatar(@user, :thumb)) %>" class="u-photo" width="150">
	</div>
	<h1>
		<a href="/" class="u-url u-uid">
			Hi, my name is <span title="\inÇ°i\" class="p-name">Inhji</span>
		</a>
	</h1>
	<h2 class="p-note"><%= @user.tagline %></h2>
</header>

<h3>A few things about me</h3>

<ul>
	<li>I got introduced to computers &amp; games at the age of 5 when I watched my dad playing <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxyd" class="external">OXYD</a> on his Atari ST</li>
	<li>I started teaching myself to code when I got a book about programming in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turbo_Pascal" class="external">Turbo Pascal</a> at 12</li>
	<li>I work as a software developer where I write windows applications with .NET</li>
	<li>In my free time I write a lot of Elixir, almost exclusively for the website you're reading</li>
	<li>My other passion besides computers is music</li>
</ul>

<h3>Latest Bookmarks</h3>

<dl>
	<%= for b <- @bookmarks do %>
	<dt><%= link b.title, to: Routes.home_path(@conn, :bookmark, b) %> <small class="brackets"><%= Timex.from_now(b.inserted_at) %></small></dt>
	<dd><%= tag_string(b.tags) %></dd>
	<% end %>
</dl>

<h3>Latest Listens</h3>

<dl>
	<%= for l <- @listens do %>
	<dt><%= l.track.name %> <small class="brackets"><%= Timex.from_now(l.listened_at) %></small></dt>
	<dd>by <%= l.artist.name %></dd>
	<% end %>
</dl>

<h3>Projects</h3>

<dl>
	<dt><%= link "Tomie", to: Routes.home_path(@conn, :project, :tomie) %> <small class="brackets">2013 - 2020</small></dt>
	<dd>Tomie is one of many attempts to build a selfhosted, universal platform for my content.</dd>	

	<dt><%= link "Eurorack", to: Routes.home_path(@conn, :project, :eurorack) %> <small class="brackets">2018 - 2020</small></dt>
	<dd>My Eurorack system aims to be a lifelong experiment on music-making as a process, not a goal.</dd>	
</dl>

<footer class="site-footer">
	<p>Created by Inhji.</p>
	<p>
		<a href="https://git.inhji.de/inhji/tomie" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source</a>
		<a href="/admin" rel="noopener noreferrer">Admin</a>
	</p>
</footer>
